{"tid":1633904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂係你呀 入黎啦 多謝你呀！","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:04:30.000Z","uid":9131,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d92aef40e3dcb4f57dc16784fa11905bfdf044b5","tid":1633904,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"過左四個月啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武多謝你！<br />\n和理非多謝你！<br />\n文宣組多謝你！<br />\n家長街坊多謝你！</span></span><br />\n好想俾啲掌聲你地，但對唔住要忍一忍手先。<br />\n因為我地未贏。<br />\n但我對出過力嘅每一位致最崇高嘅敬意<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰<br />\n大家記得嗎<br />\n口號背後我都唔可以叫到習慣哂而變成純口號<br />\n<br />\n大家睇下港共政府<br />\n佢地真係幾離譜都唔割<br />\n我地既口號唔可以俾對方做得好過我地<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有冇想多謝邊個<br />\n提一提佢 我地未贏<br />\n唔好鬆懈！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"298ea0cee0df8476bfb68c99a4fbac7fae790763","tid":1633904,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝你呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d413864871cf88c6ce713dd0ffac1bea8e73dc4d","tid":1633904,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝你呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a3aef5bed92bd98782b17ddc257436136ad8ca2","tid":1633904,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"多謝你呀！"},{"pid":"ca664dc0b1a2ebc536268b79f520efcd1421d56e","tid":1633904,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝你呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd9e7dc060da9a8b24a58a941485186421445dbf","tid":1633904,"uid":217254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><